short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Mute any google meet audio or video from any tab or window

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ever got stuck in another window or browser tab and wanted to mute or unmute your audio/video on google meet? Then this is the best solution for you. 

To mute all audios on Windows: CTRL + Shift + 0
To mute all audios on Mac: CMD + Shift + 0

To mute all videos on Windows: CTRL + Shift + 9
To mute all video on Mac: CMD + Shift + 9
